sentences.english: There were some angry exchanges between the riot police and the protestors.
sentences.chinese: 抗議民衆與鎮暴警察發生齟齬。

sentences.english: Never get into fights with ugly people! they haudio-videoe nothing to lose.
sentences.chinese: 完全不要和長得醜的齟齬，他們曾經沒什麼可輸的了。

sentences.english: All the contradictions, hard to understand.
sentences.chinese: 一切難以瞭解的矛盾齟齬。

sentences.english: So long as lovers have care for each other, discord and estrangement will be removed.
sentences.chinese: 只要彼此心中有着牽念，再多的齟齬隔閡，總會消除。

sentences.english: First, there was the brouhaha over the notification system and the drop in traffic.
sentences.chinese: 首先，通知系統和流量下跌風波中就產生了不少齟齬。
